sources.title: The Round Up (1920) ROSCOE "FATTY" ARBUCKLE
sources.description:
PizzaFLIX Presents CLASSIC MOVIE MONDAY
Stars: Fatty Arbuckle, Mabel Julienne Scott, Wallace Beery
Director: George Melford

Silent screen legend Roscoe “Fatty” Arbuckle made his feature film debut in this first-class western. 
Watch for silent film mega-star Buster Keaton in an uncredited cameo as an Apache Indian!

New 4K digital transfer and restoration of the 35mm archival master preserved by Paramount Archives and the Library of Congress. New score composed and performed by Donald Sosin!

metadata.Plot: An overweight sheriff does his best to assist a man accused of theft.
metadata.Actors: Roscoe 'Fatty' Arbuckle, Mabel Julienne Scott, Irving Cummings
